title: MIDTERMS LOOM: Oz / Fetterman and What Else To Expect.
itunes:title: MIDTERMS LOOM: Oz / Fetterman and What Else To Expect.
description: Candidates Dr. Mehmet Oz and John Fetterman faced off in a debate last night in their race for the Pennsylvania Senate. Jay, Jordan, and the Sekulow team provide their analysis of the debate as well as lay out the road ahead just two weeks out from the midterm elections. This and more today on Sekulow.
